{
  "stem": "24195.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I-- it turned out that I quit my job in the newspaper after traveling all over Germany and covering events for them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I just did some freelance writing, because now I had to make the decision.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was going to go and leave Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was-- I had relatives that were smart enough, come over here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were in Chicago, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A physician who worked-- a cousin of my father's, who worked at-- one who worked at the VA hospital in Memphis, Tennessee, or Nashville, Tennessee.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other one was here, right here, in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came over 1937-38.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, but I-- they really weren't much help.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I asked them if they would sponsor me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, well, they talked about it, talked around about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sent me a number of care packages and other things, which was nice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you couldn't get anything in Germany until 1948.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very rationed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went-- I decided I'm qualifying to be a displaced person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They changed the displaced persons thing-- requirements.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could include a German nationality, which I don't know why they didn't do it from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Harry Truman had something to do with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was present of the US then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans were-- German Jews were just as persecuted as Polish or Lithuanians and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they changed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then, then I worked for-- then I got a job, a job offer to work the last six months before my-- it takes about six months to get processed-- with the-- for the Joint Distribution Committee in Munich, at Munich headquarters.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was, was a very accommodating, because that was the agency that was going to take me through all the steps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they decided it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
